  "detailed_description": "TUBMLE, an online multiplayer fun type stunt racing game, where you can play with your friends and family or play with bots in single-player, it's a really fun to play game with challenging race tracks and maps, so play Tumble Now!<br><br><strong>CONTROLS:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>W,A,S,D To Move The Car</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>R To Restart From The Last Waypoint, Or Reset The Car</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Escape To Pause The Game</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>T to Enable Slomo Mode</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234310/extras/56d2b5d82607a26704e90c1b167dbdd5.avif?t=1748527040\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiplayer Mode</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play With Your Friends!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenging Race!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New Maps In Every Update</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Slowmo Camera Mode!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-Player With AI!</li></ul>",
